</div>
<p style="margin-bottom:16px"><strong>Xixuan Collins</strong> is the author of the novel <em>Flowing Water, Falling Flowers</em> (MWC Press, 2020) and a finalist in the Black Lawrence Press Immigrant Writing Series. Her writings have appeared in <em>PastTen</em>, <em>Overachiever Magazine</em>, <em>London Reader</em>, <em>Zibby Mag</em>, and others. She is a regular contributor to <em>Asian Cha: A Literary Journal</em>.</p>
